description: Product Description These seedling pots are ideal for plants, such as leeks, parsnips, cucumbers and broad beans. The seeds are planted individually in each pot and allowed to develop into young plants. When it's time to plant, the set can just be put into the soil where the plant will mature. What is a seed pot? These are seedling pots made from of paper pulp These pots offer a user-friendly way of starting seeds or seedlings, they can be planted directly into the soil, reducing the risk of injury to the seedling roots, as the plant is not disturbed when transplanted into your garden soil. Say goodbye to transplant shock and root circulation Like any farmer or gardening enthusiast, planting seedlingsis a difficult business. They often need to be grown in a small pot and then transplanted - It is complex process. These beautiful pots are here, however, to provide a simple solution. Simply grow your seedlings, then plant them in your yard or garden without removing them from the pots. No transplant shock, no root circulation, and no wilted plants and flowers - it's that simple.
